==English==

===Noun===
'''Communication mix''' 

# Describes the range of approaches and expressions of a marketing idea developed with the hope that it be effective in conveying the ideas to the diverse population of people who receive it.
#:You must know how to use the elements of the communications mix to communicate the product’s existence, value and benefits to the target customers.
